    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are explicitly excluded by the MRL 2 assessment matrix. Grid convergence, output comparison against the FDA benchmark dataset, and direct relevance of the hemolysis QoI to the CPB COU collectively provide sufficient confidence that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all 5 operating points. Decision: Accepted.",
